    <div class="explanation">
      <p>The <a href="https://chris-sarli.github.io/parking-analysis/">Downtown Providence Parking</a> site is an exhaustive inventory of parking in Downtown Providence, Rhode Island.</p>
      <p>The goal of the project is to produce visuals and statistics showing that far too much space is devoted to parking in the city&rsquo;s core and that changes need to be made.</p>
      <p>I collected most of the data myself, added it to <a href="http://openstreetmap.org">OpenStreetMap</a> for anyone to use, and built this overview from that data.</p>
