    <p><a href="https://chris.sarl/station-search/">Station Search</a> is a page I put together for <a href="https://cs.brown.edu/courses/info/csci1300/">a UI/UX class</a> in 2019. The only thing it does is list all 272 stations on the London Underground and provide some basic tools to sort, filter, and search these station listings.</p>
